➜手贱搜了下吴京的现状....被吓到了
http://www.sohu.com/a/415857011_117993	3621
<p class="ql-align-center">不得不承认</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">男人一到了中年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">似乎就逃不了发福变胖的情况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不管你曾经的颜值有多巅峰肌肉再好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在岁月面前，绝大部分都得任其宰割</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200901/0af24815cab341dca07a5c6c5c413077.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>比如前段时间</p>
<p><strong>硬汉吴京就因为大肚腩而引发热议</strong></p>
<p>只见他撩起衣服跟于谦老师相谈甚欢</p>
<p>不经意间暴露出了自己的啤酒肚</p>
<p>▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=212663969&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p>由于大肚腩过于饱满膨胀</p>
<p>体贴的网友有些心疼他</p>
<p>还给打了码，哈哈哈</p>
<p>▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200901/52d8730daac24973b5676fe8ce6d02cb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
